{"id": 2543, "genre": 1001, "title": "你爸妈为了和同龄人保持一致都干过啥事？", "description": "你们是和老姐妹兄弟站在同一起跑线上了，可苦了我了…来，谈谈爸妈的 peer pressure。（题图来自：iStock ©️ cosmaa）", "record_count": 1218, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20180926093008kXrHqCL3jFgy2v4f.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-10-02T17:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 303376, "content": "逼我赶紧结婚", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1467893}, {"id": 302369, "content": "催婚", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1462725}, {"id": 302632, "content": "看见别的阿姨做了电子相册（那种飞照片带音乐的），要求我也给她的相册做一个。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 868692}, {"id": 302377, "content": "一直没离婚", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1461850}, {"id": 302122, "content": "我爸玩起来了抖音，好像是吧233", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 416657}, {"id": 302133, "content": "买了辆山地车，经常早起去骑行。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1461334}, {"id": 302915, "content": "学习广场舞", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1229774}, {"id": 301896, "content": "微信家族群、七大姑八大姨每人每天定点儿推送养生小文章和各种莲花图片（ーー；）", "image": null, "praise_count": 182, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 993028}, {"id": 301897, "content": "只要是别人家新有的或可炫耀的。¯\\_(ツ)_/¯", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1429934}, {"id": 301898, "content": "熟知各种保健品……", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 906369}, {"id": 301900, "content": "和朋友出去自驾游，一路欢唱样板戏选段，多数表示曾对艺术很向往", "image": null, "praise_count": 36, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1454337}, {"id": 301902, "content": "跟我要各大视频网站vip😂", "image": null, "praise_count": 37, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1082087}, {"id": 301904, "content": "我爸希望我快点生孩子，让他“升级”当外公，他周围的朋友都有第三代了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 42, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1459464}, {"id": 305745, "content": "微信表情包一定要和小姐妹同款。发在微信群里面的视频一定要足够恶俗搞笑画面一定要丑。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1387663}, {"id": 301906, "content": "“吃完把鸡蛋壳留下，我碾成末喝，补钙。”", "image": null, "praise_count": 26, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 950214}, {"id": 303187, "content": "买房", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1464277}, {"id": 301910, "content": "有多少年轻人是为了趋同再也不用QQ的，都一样", "image": null, "praise_count": 85, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 869835}, {"id": 301911, "content": "买手机不会用", "image": null, "praise_count": 51, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1427418}, {"id": 301914, "content": "男生割", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1456683}, {"id": 301915, "content": "劝不住要参加低价港澳游，然后买了一堆没什么用的三无产品回来。", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1026074}, {"id": 301916, "content": "听说我去看了华晨宇演唱会\n我爸我妈跑去听了一天的华晨宇的歌", "image": null, "praise_count": 51, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1455479}, {"id": 301919, "content": "买房", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1350649}, {"id": 301921, "content": "拍照必备：墨镜纱巾帽子套装，以及像舞台上亮相的pose", "image": null, "praise_count": 32, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1459589}, {"id": 301923, "content": "对一切新鲜事物持严重怀疑态度，对一切便捷支付都小心翼翼，", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1183687}, {"id": 301925, "content": "微信群里 每到过节 就一定要群主发红包😂", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1459653}, {"id": 301927, "content": "相亲相爱一家人，各种养生和不能吃", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1447737}, {"id": 302184, "content": "我妈穿上了一条花碎裙，还搭了一双小皮鞋", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1449065}, {"id": 306025, "content": "坚定支持崔永元(……)", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1479888}, {"id": 301930, "content": "晒娃（也就是我）", "image": null, "praise_count": 20, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 705724}, {"id": 301932, "content": "我妈硬是要去跳广场舞一天都不落的。说这是她们这个年龄里的潮流趋势，谁该不会跳几个舞啊！", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1455021}, {"id": 301933, "content": "跟微信相关的，可以说是非常有同感了", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1121362}, {"id": 301934, "content": "催特么婚...", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 761046}, {"id": 301935, "content": "退休之后带着狗子四处旅游完全不管我的生死", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1394604}, {"id": 301936, "content": "狂拍照、狂P图、狂发圈儿…", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1458727}, {"id": 301937, "content": "他们成了我眼里的无所事事，不求上进 好吃懒做 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 23, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 275723}, {"id": 300403, "content": "互发拼多多链接“帮我砍一刀”", "image": null, "praise_count": 105, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 300404, "content": "跳不来舞，但为了获知邻里最新动态每天去附近超市门口蹦一会", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 300405, "content": "报名参加“天上掉馅饼”式廉价旅行团，“老李老王都一起去，能有啥问题”", "image": null, "praise_count": 71, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 300406, "content": "你王大娘家的二孙子都两岁了，你的到底啥时候领对象回家？", "image": null, "praise_count": 252, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 301942, "content": "我妈跟阿姨们一起去跳广场舞啦。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1056675}, {"id": 302716, "content": "开始运用微信自带emoji比如呲牙笑，捂嘴笑等等…", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1464753}, {"id": 304000, "content": "急责要你结婚，", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1471449}, {"id": 301955, "content": "楼下阿姨说新买的净水器很好用，果断买了一个把以前那个扔在一边，连摆放位置都一样", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1458399}, {"id": 301958, "content": "各种文章链接转朋友圈，喊着家里人阅读那金币…", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1459917}, {"id": 301959, "content": "“开心一家人”微信群", "image": null, "praise_count": 57, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1459935}, {"id": 302472, "content": "看中国有嘻哈ヽ(。_°)ノ", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1455118}, {"id": 301961, "content": "跟风买衣服", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1459221}, {"id": 301966, "content": "发红包让我买心仪已久的迪奥999", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1458877}, {"id": 301970, "content": "我爸妈发的养生的公众号文章都看了……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1459978}, {"id": 301971, "content": "整天广场舞，还有跳舞组建的微信群，聊的也是热火朝天", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1451151}]}